6/16/21 at 7:27 a.m.- A flood watch will be in effect today from 10 a.m. to 8 p.m. EDT as additional rounds of heavy rainfall are possible, mostly for the Gulf coast/metro areas as well as Miami-Dade/Broward Counties.
